<iitk>rAFci teVst pottiyil virAt koliyinY wolYpattEyil kAyamerYpattawu , awanYE parikAcam ceVyyum viwamAka cila ceVykEkalYE Asi.vIrarkalY ceVywawAka eVlYYunwulYlYa carccEyil koliyE ameVrikka awipar tramputanY oVppittu ‘ ulaka vilYEyAttinY tramp AkirYAr virAt koli ’ eVnYrYu varNiwwulYlYawu wi teVyli teVlikirAp eVnYrYa Afkila Utakam innilEyil , afkulYlYa pilYAstik woVlYYirYcAlE oVnYrYil witIreVnYa wI vipawwu erYpattawu . </iitk>

