<iitk>kAlnatEkalYE parAmarikka mutiyAwa vivacAyikalY , katanwa cila vArafkalYAka awika alYavil mAtukalYE virYpanYEkku koVNtu varukinYrYanYar innilEyil , inwu camaya arYanilEyaw wurYE iNE ANEyar kajenwiranYinY uwwaravup pati , uwavi ANEyarkalY FAnYacekaranY , jIvAnYanwam , mAriyappanY , kumpakoNam vattAtciyar kArwwikeyanY , minYvAriyaw wurYEyinYar nerYrYu polIsArinY pAwukApputanY poVrYrYAmarEk kulYakkarEyil Akkiramippu ceVyyappattirunwa 9 katEkalYE poVklEnY mUlam akarYrYinYar . </iitk>

